<%- include('partials/header') %>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);
    padding: 70px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  [data-theme="dark"] .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #020617 0%, #0F172A 100%); }
  .page-hero-icon {
    width: 70px; height: 70px; border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(0,102,255,0.15);
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 18px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 5vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: #FFFFFF; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .page-content { padding: 56px 0; background: var(--bg-body); }
  .content-wrapper { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  
  .policy-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: clamp(20px, 4vw, 32px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .policy-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
  .policy-card h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.3rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .policy-card h2 i { color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .policy-card p { color: var(--text-body); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .policy-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .policy-card ul li {
    padding: 8px 0; color: var(--text-body); font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px;
  }
  .policy-card ul li i { color: var(--success); margin-top: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  
  .highlight-box {
    background: var(--primary-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,102,255,0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .highlight-box i { color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .highlight-box span { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero { padding: 48px 0; }
    .page-hero-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .page-content { padding: 36px 0; }
    .policy-card { padding: 20px; }
    .policy-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .policy-card ul li { font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .highlight-box { padding: 14px 16px; }
  }
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck-fast"></i></div>
  <h1 class="page-hero-title">Delivery Policy</h1>
</div>

<div class="page-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Where We Deliver</h2>
        <p>ShopNest delivers to all 25 districts across Sri Lanka. We partner with reliable local courier services to ensure your orders reach you safely, whether you're in Colombo or Jaffna, Galle or Trincomalee.</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
          <span>Island-wide delivery available to all districts in Sri Lanka 🇱🇰</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Processing Time</h2>
        <p>All orders are processed within <strong>1-2 business days</strong> after payment confirmation. You will receive a confirmation email with your order details once your order is placed.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Order processing: 1-2 business days</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Orders placed before 3:00 PM processed same day</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Weekend orders processed on Monday</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i> Delivery Times & Rates</h2>
        <p>Delivery times vary depending on your location. Below are our estimated delivery timeframes within Sri Lanka:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <strong>Colombo & Suburbs:</strong> 1-3 business days</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <strong>Major Cities (Kandy, Galle, Jaffna, etc.):</strong> 2-5 business days</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <strong>Other Areas:</strong> 3-7 business days</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Delivery costs are calculated at checkout based on your order and location</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Free delivery is available on orders meeting our threshold amount</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Tracking information is provided once your order is dispatched</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-search-location"></i> Tracking Your Order</h2>
        <p>Once your order is dispatched, you will receive a tracking number via email. You can track your order anytime by visiting our <a href="/track" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;">Track Order</a> page and entering your tracking number.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Important Notes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Delivery times are estimates and may vary during holidays, adverse weather, or unforeseen circumstances.</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Please ensure your delivery address and phone number are correct for smooth delivery.</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Our courier partners will attempt delivery twice before returning the package.</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> If your package is marked as delivered but you haven't received it, please contact us immediately.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>